Introduction

Lil Cherry (릴체리) is a South Korean rapper who debuted under Wedaplugg Records in 2018, was part of Hedon Entertainment in 2019, and is currently at SAUCE CARTEL since 2020. She is the sister of Goldbuuda (Jito Mo). She debuted in July 27, 2018 with the song 'Motorola' alongside GOLDBUUDA.
